
Author: Thomas Moerwald (Vienna University of Technology)
Email: moerwald@acin.tuwien.ac.at

API: TMGLWindow.h
	
Event Definition: TMGLEvent.h
Input Definition: TMGLInput.h

This is a platform independent OpenGL Window Managment library for creating, updating and destroying OpenGL Windows and handling keyboard/mouse input control

	* requirements
		- OpenGL, GLU, glew
